OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold and quite cloudy start
OL,6,Fwith perhaps the odd spot of rain over
OL,7,FFife. Otherwise dry with increasingly
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells, but feeling
OL,9,Fcooler than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry throughout
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight. Clear skies
OL,13,Fat first, but high cloud spreading in
OL,14,Ffrom the west later. Overnight frost
OL,15,Fdeveloping.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAfter a chilly start with
OL,18,Fovernight frost it will be another dry
OL,19,Fand bright day and feeling a bit
OL,20,Fmilder again. Becoming cloudier at
OL,21,Ftimes in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
